metadata.name: ShibasWorld #40
metadata.description:
ShibasWorld is where all the Shiba's I create, from every universe live. Think of it like the Multiverse of Madness but with Shiba's, Shiba Human Hybrids, etc! Commissions also available for Personalized Shiba's Collection. 

20% of all sales go to Newcollar.co a non profit animal rescue in Ontario Canada.

5% Allocated for the ShibBurn Portal.

Roadmap and more at linktr.ee/cryptonicog  
Stay Tuned we are building!
